name: Tezzy Everydays #2 | HODL Ape | May 8th, 2021
description: This is the second day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. I decided to go with a King Kong inspired piece for today. Growing up outside of Boston in the early 80's, the King Kong remake with Jessica Lange and Jeff Bridges was constantly reran on channel 56's "Creature Double Feature". Watching this film as a kid influenced me in a major way. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
